s/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S以前可能鐘意小龍女覺我好文靜但現實根本唔會有呢種人+ 呢種人應該好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"好同意 睇郭靖會好燥 超煩依種太過戇直既大好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:24:07.000Z","msg":"楊過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超鍾意佢個鐘亦正亦邪的性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e470d2d134a3d6277d7b658dd7c71eccf452d83","tid":870981,"uid":84128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天山童姥"},{"pid":"89df31110dcbb54f7d3edb35e37c5edafd538294","tid":870981,"uid":191346,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:58:12.000Z","msg":"木婉清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a716ccb3f6bc8065fd6149b26f15a69bf20f01","tid":870981,"uid":189432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"無人鍾意韋小寶咩"},{"pid":"ea533a5cc58dc59f76ad084566ac8cfbde9b302f","tid":870981,"uid":121222,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0054cc2ceaf95112b3a7dda1081d6150d034f5d1","tid":870981,"uid":8246,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"裘千尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:12:45.000Z","msg":"c兄 識玩 <br />\n佢含棗嘅功夫，威震武林<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3462d7e517f7e9a54400d06b8fc326698355aa01","tid":870981,"uid":56212,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"段譽"},{"pid":"5264a2657ef75e3f19a45c20b869efdea5a93c88","tid":870981,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"令狐