10-22T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"過了一會，李秋水又輕輕說道：「師哥，你聰明絕頂，卻又癡得絕頂，為什麼愛上了你自己手雕的玉像，卻不愛那會說、會笑、會動、會愛你的師妹？你心中把這玉像當成了我小妹子，是不是？我喝這玉像的醋，跟你鬧翻了，出去找了許多俊秀的少年郎君來，在你面前跟他們調情，於是你就此一怒而去，再也不回來了。師哥，其實你不用生氣，那些美少年一個個都給我殺了，沉在湖底，你可知道麼？」<br />\n...<br />\n突然尖聲叫道：「師姊，你我兩個都是可憐蟲，都&hellip;&hellip;都&hellip;&hellip;教這沒良心的給騙了，哈哈，哈哈，哈哈！」她大笑三聲，身子一仰，翻倒在地。<br />\n<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6253eedc4aedfd9f060588ba459de4e8b2e74c3a","tid":870981,"uid":130901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"田伯光"},{"pid":"d2fafd5896d7c64c487c181730335036c6870512","tid":870981,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"蕭峰"},{"pid":"e94bf7836d0917f55735da6fa3f1c8b10b9d1a01","tid":870981,"uid":37721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"小昭"},{"pid":"f15f84c94181f42fd375b42ae02b999cf7d5a949","tid":870981,"uid":184699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"男：胡一刀<br />\n女：殷素素，射鵰黃蓉"},{"pid":"967a97c212884953ba1900d87cc45df354617ed5","tid":870981,"uid":81380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"以前係胡斐<br />\n大左就係楊過<br />\n專意佢夠專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd836ab463afee8ce4d89d8c7b8fd6c876e8694","tid":870981,"uid":81380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"967a97c212884953ba1900d87cc45df354617ed5","tid":870981,"uid":81380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"以前係胡斐<br />\n大左就係楊過<br />\n專意佢夠專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"鍾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf4a5688c793344b92573bfd2b665c62c861a6b","tid":870981,"uid":36372,