":0,"quote":{"pid":"a27390be89a9c9740d75aee2e66e30497917fd07","tid":870981,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ecd779286daee24883e988fba0014c05618e0242","tid":870981,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"康敏<br />\n<br />\n又衰格又賤又淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"邊個畀腐皮，人各有所好都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:20:01.000Z","msg":"有人正皮左 開心返未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10042e63ec531427d58000f580a32b6bbec7ea80","tid":870981,"uid":92811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48ea71e5d0017170c31ba4a67b0b31087cb1daaf","tid":870981,"uid":50060,"like":6,"dislike":14,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"男既就係楊過<br />\n<br />\n因為我唔信現實根本真係有D 郭靖/張無盈 咁純品咁戇居既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經去到IQ80<br />\n<br />\n楊過就係由細 聰明到大<br />\n年少輕狂 靚仔但係專一<br />\n去到後尾仲變到好有俠既風範 一齊守城<br />\n<br />\n最後同 姑姑一齊番屋企 專一到尾<br />\n<br />\n令狐沖都聰明 但係無 楊過咁有勇氣 同埋 傲氣<br />\n<br />\n女主角就係 射雕黃蓉/趙敏/任盈盈 <br />\n三個女仔都係聰明 同肯為左自己個男人 做好多事在所不辭<br />\n但係前兩者 性格比較「激烈」? 有時係會覺得煩左少少<br />\n任盈盈岩岩 &quot;合&quot;到好處<br />\n<br />\n耍嬌時耍嬌<br />\n要靜時會靜<br />\n要幫男主角既時候 可以心狠手辣<br />\n但最後佢都係為你好 佢都係愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S以前可能鐘意小龍女覺我好文靜但現實根本唔會有呢種人+ 呢種人應該好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"令狐冲點會無傲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寧死都唔想受人施舍，拒投少林<br />\n5派大勢已去都唔投降外父<br />\n<br />\n連盈盈都怕佢唔肯學易筋經"},{"pid":